title: Hooveriii - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Hooveriii performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded August 10, 2022.

Bert Hoover - Guitar / Vocals
Kaz Mirblouk - Bass / Vocals
Gabe “Baby Gabe” Salomon - Synth
Matt Zuk  - Guitar / Vocals
Jon Modaff - Drums

Host: Cheryl Waters
Audio Engineer: Jon Roberts
Mastering: Matt Ogaz
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro & Scott Holpainen
Editor: Jim Beckmann
